## 11. IF SOMETHING IS BROKEN — CHECKLIST

- App not starting? → pm2 logs flixcam-production; check .env and that npm ci + npm run build ran.
- Build failing? → autoprefixer/postcss/typescript in dependencies; storage/uploads symlink; run scripts/build-with-uploads-workaround.sh.
- Deploy not working? → Confirm PRODUCTION_APP_PATH; run all 5 deploy steps; PM2 cwd correct.
- Wrong path somewhere? → Check paths.config.sh; grep for "apps/production" or "/home/flixcam/app" in .sh, .js, .md and fix any that are not historical comments.
